comments: Gay (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by DeRozan (SAS).
Gay (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) places a resting forearm on Forbes' (SAS) body, but he does not extend it or apply force during his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in White's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gay (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Fournier's (ORL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fournier (ORL) makes marginal contact to White's (SAS) chest as he uses the screen, but the contact does not dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in DeRozan's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gay (SAS) hops consecutively on the same foot after he has gathered the ball.
Fultz (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position during the drive and jump shot attempt by Gay (SAS).
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).

Fultz (ORL) cleanly deflects the pass away from White (SAS).  White then regains control and starts his dribble off of Fournier's (ORL) planted foot.  As the ball is loose, Fournier makes marginal contact to White's arm while both players go for the loose ball.
Mills (SAS) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Fournier's (ORL) leg that affects his driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) makes marginal contact to Gordon's (ORL) back as Forbes (SAS) simultaneously cleanly tips the ball away.
